node.title: Person critically injured in shooting in Auckland CBD
node.description: Police say someone was shot and critically injured in central Auckland last night.
node.content:
["Police say someone was shot and critically injured in central Auckland last night.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123RF\n
", "They say gunshots were fired at an address in Wellesley Street West, a busy part of the central city.", "It happened at about 11.15pm, and shortly afterwards, someone turned up at hospital with gunshot wounds.", "They are in a critical condition, but stable.", "Police are at the scene this morning, and asking for assistance from anyone who can help find the offenders."]
